 s/2024/03/New-Leala.jpg
UID:JGPnxTSCmAXEX9Oo2P70g
SUMMARY:Texas Sound Meditation with Leala\, Melissa\, and James
DTSTAMP:20260616T174851Z
DTSTART:20260616T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Levy Park brings “Self Care” to a whole new level with Sound He
	aling led by Leala\, Melissa\, and James. \nA sound bath is a gentle\, nur
	turing\, and cathartic meditation experience for anyone looking to improve
	 the quality of their life. This act of self-care is beneficial for anyone
	 from beginners to advanced meditators who are ready to experience a great
	er sense of peace and well-being. \nThe Levy Park Sound Baths will assist 
	in clearing out that which is blocking the natural vitality while strength
	ening the connection and balance between mind\, body\, and soul. A collect
	ively cultivated safe space offers participants an opportunity to deepen t
	heir own journey of self-love\, healing or transformation. \nWhile relievi
	ng stress\, tension and anxiety this sound immersion experience will have 
	you feeling revitalized\, relaxed and rejuvenate. Let the sounds wash away
	 everything that no longer serves you as you set your intentions and manif
	est your desires! \n \n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/sound-ther
	apy-texas-sound/2026-06-16/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/sound-therapy-texas-sound/2026-0
	6-16/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
